---
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.astro"
import SiteHeader from "@/components/site-header"
import SiteFooter from "@/components/site-footer.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Модул: Организација — Veridex ERP"
  description="Компании, вработени, возила, приколки и одржување. Сè што вашиот бизнис поседува и управува — на едно место."
>
  <SiteHeader client:load currentPath="/moduli/organizacija" />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-transparent to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275_/_0.05)]"></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary">
            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-xs font-bold text-white">1</span>
            Модул
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
            Целата организација
            <span class="text-gradient"> на дланка</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Компании, вработени, возила, приколки и нивното одржување &mdash;
            сè што вашиот бизнис поседува и управува, на едно место.
          </p>
          <a href="/kontakt" class="mt-8 inline-block">
            <button class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275)] px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-primary/25 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
              Закажи демо
            </button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Што вклучува</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
            Пет области за целосна контрола над сè што вашиот бизнис поседува.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Компании -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-white p-8">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3H21" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold">Компании</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Повеќе правни субјекти, еден преглед. Секоја компанија со
              свои банкарски сметки и документи.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Основни податоци и регистрација</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Банкарски сметки по компанија</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Поврзани документи</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Вработени -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-white p-8">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold">Вработени</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Договори, позиции, плати и возачки казни &mdash;
              целосна евиденција за секој член на тимот.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Лични податоци и договори</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Плати и историја на примања</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Возачки казни и документи</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Возила -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-white p-8">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-3 0m3 0h1.125c.621 0 1.129-.504 1.09-1.124a17.902 17.902 0 0 0-3.213-9.193 2.056 2.056 0 0 0-1.58-.86H14.25M16.5 18.75h-2.25m0-11.177v-.958c0-.568-.422-1.048-.987-1.106a48.554 48.554 0 0 0-10.026 0 1.106 1.106 0 0 0-.987 1.106v7.635m12-6.677v6.677m0 4.5v-4.5m0 0h-12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold">Возила</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Целосна историја за секое возило &mdash; од регистрација до
              последен технички преглед. Правила за одржување вклучени.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Регистарски податоци и документи</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Рокови за регистрација и осигурување</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Правила за одржување</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Приколки -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-white p-8">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 16.875h3.375m0 0h3.375m-3.375 0V13.5m0 3.375v3.375M6 10.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V6a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3.75 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 10.5Zm0 9.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 10.5 18v-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 20.25Zm9.75-9.75H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V6A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 3.75h-2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 13.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold">Приколки</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Приклучна опрема евидентирана и следена со своја
              документација и рокови.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Евиденција и регистрација</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Документи и рокови</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Поврзаност со тури</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Одржување -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-white p-8 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17 17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0 0 21 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 1 1-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-6.336 4.486c.049.58.025 1.193-.14 1.743" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold">Одржување на возила</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Сервисна историја, ставки, поврзани фактури. Никогаш повеќе
              пропуштен сервис или заборавен технички преглед.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Записи за сервис со детални ставки</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Поврзаност со влезни фактури</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Автоматски потсетници</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-muted/30 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
          Подготвени да ја средите
          <span class="text-gradient"> организацијата?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
          Видете го модулот во акција со бесплатна демонстрација.
        </p>
        <a href="/kontakt" class="mt-8 inline-block">
          <button class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275)] px-10 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-2xl shadow-primary/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
            <span class="relative z-10">Закажи бесплатно демо</span>
            <div class="animate-shimmer absolute inset-0 -z-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div>
          </button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</Layout>
